ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectOrder approving the transfer of Justice Étienne Parent to the district of Québec
PrecisOrder advising that the HONOURABLE ÉTIENNE PARENT, a Judge of the Superior Court of Quebec for the district of Saint-Maurice, be appointed a Judge of the Superior Court of Quebec for the district of Québec, with residence in the territory of Ville de Québec or the immediate vicinity of that territory, effective September 1, 2024.
